description.en:
1. Overview University of Tartu Institute of Computer Science graduation theses requirements and criteria;
2. Recommendations for Estonian-language academic writing;
3. The research topic selection and preparation of a work plan;
4. Introducing one's topic at a discussion seminar together with getting and giving feedback;
5. Instructions for completing a literature review;
6. The use of citations and references;
7. Quotations and summaries, citation systems;
8. Plagiarism, the causes of plagiarism and prevention of it with the help of electronic plagiarism detection methods;
10. Instructions for making a good defence presentation;
11. Pre-defence rehearsal together with giving and receiving feedback.

